    |               | ---------+---------------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    | Expires       | Optional |                                                   | The date/time after which the response is considered stale.
    +---------------+----------+---------------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    */

